br />\n供應商 r 贊助仲撚仆街，大時大節要 r，年尾要 r，新年又要 r <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。仲要叫 d 廚師whatsapp比供應商sale，r 埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />內容其實同翠華差唔多，如果唔肯比支票回贈，就即刻轉供應商。<br />\n<br />\n講緊你呀！大喜X<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、滿X<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bd7467069b321a5a03ad72a737802e3263af8b","tid":1844490,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:13:15.000Z","msg":"蘋果話取消上市原因係因為公開發售同國際配售都唔夠數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ce9ea90a454114db609054d4c97a49d2f821d0","tid":1844490,"uid":151539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62bd7467069b321a5a03ad72a737802e3263af8b","tid":1844490,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:13:15.000Z","msg":"蘋果話取消上市原因係因為公開發售同國際配售都唔夠數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:20:29.000Z","msg":"無人要呢d垃圾股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae128d4749839cd4b9c2575bcb5819017e572d18","tid":1844490,"uid":90714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c0b267fe58cbe325740f64efb9460a9ae276fe0","tid":1844490,"uid":52273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21538c016d156481bc834649a1a27819f9e3b849","tid":1844490,"uid":55445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ce8adf9eebfa96ff878b6bfb9e6063818bf390f","tid":1844490,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T0